headline: Centene, QuidelOrtho, iRhythm, and Bio-Techne Shares Skyrocket, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks jumped in the afternoon session after news of a new government prescription drug policy and a landmark deal with Pfizer eased investor concerns over stricter pricing regulations.

headline: Could Spatial Biology Advances Shape Bio-Techne's (TECH) Long-Term Position in Precision Medicine?
summary: In September 2025, Bio-Techne Corporation unveiled new advancements in its spatial biology portfolio, enhancing its RNAscope ISH technology and Lunaphore COMET systems, to enable simultaneous RNA and protein biomarker detection on the same tissue section for translational research and clinical diagnostics. These innovations, presented at the National Society of Histotechnology Convention, highlight the increasing role of spatial biology tools in improving disease diagnosis, especially when...

headline: 3 Low-Volatility Stocks That Concern Us
summary: Low-volatility stocks may offer stability, but that often comes at the cost of slower growth and the upside potential of more dynamic companies.
